## Policy patterns

- **`is_household_member(p_household_id uuid)`** — `SECURITY DEFINER` stable; used on `households` SELECT/UPDATE.
- **Member EXISTS** — `EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM household_members hm WHERE hm.household_id = … AND hm.user_id = auth.uid())` on most household-scoped tables.
- **`recurring_payment_reports`** — `member_own_reports` (ALL on own `household_member_id`); `payer_read_reports` (SELECT when user is recurring expense payer).
- **Storage** (`storage.objects`) — authenticated INSERT per bucket; public SELECT per bucket.

