## Functions & triggers

| Name | Signature | Notes |
|------|-----------|--------|
| `is_household_member` | `(p_household_id uuid) → boolean` | RLS helper; SECURITY DEFINER |
| `create_household` | `(p_name text) → json` | Atomically creates household + creator member; **not used in app** (see `app/api/households/route.ts` two-step insert) |
| `update_updated_at` | trigger fn | Sets `updated_at = now()` |

**Trigger:** `recipes_updated_at` BEFORE UPDATE ON `recipes` → `update_updated_at()`.

