## Domain reference (key columns & constraints)

### Core

- **`households`** — `id`, `name`, `invite_code` (unique), `image_url`, `created_at`
- **`household_members`** — FK `household_id`, `user_id` → auth.users; `nickname`, `is_rent_owner`; unique `(household_id, user_id)`

### Finances (⚠️ no RLS)

- **`expense_categories`** — `household_id`, `name`, `paid_by_member_id`; unique `(household_id, name)`
- **`category_splits`** — `category_id`, `household_member_id`, `percentage` (0–100); unique `(category_id, household_member_id)`
- **`expenses`** — `household_id`, `category_id`, `description`, `total_amount`, `date`, `receipt_id`, `recurring_expense_id`; payer: `paid_by_member_id` (nullable) **or** `paid_by_guest_id`
- **`expense_splits`** — `expense_id`, `calculated_amount`, `is_settled`, `percentage_override`; split target: `household_member_id` **or** `guest_id` (nullable member); unique `(expense_id, household_member_id)`
- **`recurring_expenses`** — `amount`, `due_day_of_month` (1–28), `alert_days_before`, `is_active`, `color`, `paid_by_member_id`
- **`recurring_expense_splits`** — `percentage`, optional `amount`; unique `(recurring_expense_id, household_member_id)`
- **`recurring_payment_reports`** — unique `(recurring_expense_id, household_member_id, cycle_due_date)` for idempotency

### Guests (✅ RLS)

- **`household_guests`** — `name`, `email`, `expires_at`, `created_by` → member
- **`household_guest_groups`** + **`household_guest_group_members`** — group membership; unique `(group_id, guest_id)`

### Receipts (✅ RLS)

- **`receipts`** — `uploaded_by_member_id`, `image_url`, `merchant_name`, `receipt_date`, `raw_total`, `ai_extracted_data`
- **`receipt_line_items`** — `receipt_id`, `description`, `amount`, `quantity`

### Catalog (✅ RLS on items/aliases)

- **`household_items`** — `name`, `default_category_id`, `split_overrides` jsonb, `image_url`; unique `(household_id, name)`
- **`household_item_aliases`** — `alias_text`, `display_text`; unique `(household_id, alias_text)`

### Recipes (⚠️ no RLS)

- **`recipes`** — `created_by` → auth.users, `category_tag`, `updated_at` (trigger)
- **`recipe_ingredients`** — `quantity` is **text** (not numeric)
- **`recipe_steps`** — unique `(recipe_id, step_number)`
- **`recipe_tags`** — unique `(household_id, name)`

### Shopping (⚠️ no RLS)

- **`shopping_lists`** — `owner_type` enum; `user_id` or `household_id` per owner
- **`shopping_list_items`** — `quantity`, `unit`, `is_checked`

### Calendar

- **`meal_logs`** — `recipe_id`, `made_by_member_id`, `made_at` (date)
- **`household_events`** — `date`, `title` (1–100 chars), `note`, `created_by` → member

