## Relationship map

```
auth.users
  └── household_members ──► households
        ├── expense_categories ──► category_splits ◄──► members
        │     └── expenses ──► expense_splits ◄── members | guests
        │           ├── receipts ──► receipt_line_items
        │           └── recurring_expenses ──► recurring_expense_splits
        │                 └── recurring_payment_reports
        ├── household_guests ──► guest_groups / group_members
        ├── household_items ──► household_item_aliases
        ├── recipes ──► ingredients, steps | recipe_tags
        ├── shopping_lists ──► shopping_list_items
        ├── meal_logs, household_events
        └── (finances/shopping/recipes: 12 tables without RLS)
auth.users ──► shopping_lists [owner_type = user]
```

