## Code integration

| Layer | Import | Use when |
|-------|--------|----------|
| Server (RLS) | `@/lib/supabase/server` `createClient()` | Routes, server components, most services |
| Browser | `@/lib/supabase/client` | Auth session, storage uploads |
| Admin | `@/lib/supabase/admin` `createAdminClient()` | Bypasses RLS — registration, guest emails, bill-reminder cron, privileged joins; **never client-side** |
| Services | `@/lib/services/*` | Business logic / DB access |
| Types | `@/lib/types/*` | Domain shapes |
| HTTP (UI) | `@/lib/api/client` | Client components only |

### Table → service map

| Tables | Service |
|--------|---------|
| `households`, `household_members` | `lib/services/households.ts` |
| Finances stack + `recurring_payment_reports` | `lib/services/finances.ts`, `lib/services/billReminderEmails.ts` |
| `receipts`, `receipt_line_items` | `lib/services/receipts.ts` |
| `household_items`, `household_item_aliases` | `lib/services/householdItems.ts` |
| Guest tables | `lib/services/guests.ts` |
| `recipes`, `recipe_*`, `recipe_tags` | `lib/services/recipes.ts` |
| `meal_logs` + calendar reads (`household_events`, bills, receipts) | `lib/services/mealLogs.ts` |
| `shopping_lists`, `shopping_list_items` | `lib/services/shopping.ts` |
| Dashboard aggregate | `lib/services/dashboard.ts` |

**Exception:** `app/api/dashboard/[householdId]/events/*.ts` queries `household_events` in the route — prefer extracting to a service when editing.

**Migrations:** `supabase/migrations/` (history); live DB may differ until migrations are applied everywhere.

